{"tid":485311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Now TV直播64場世界盃　ViuTV免費播19場","createTime":"2017-12-01T00:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T10:51:07.000Z","uid":142405,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf910df69d657936e468d22e5176f8bbe888ece","tid":485311,"uid":142405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:43:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20171130/57523069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F57523069&d=tM%2Bj00NxWG6U68T3aQiAS8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5ce3e3f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F57523069&h=4c5c9fd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20171130/57523069</a>（蘋果日報）<br />\n<br />\n2018年俄羅斯世界盃轉播權終有著落，電訊盈科今早宣佈，Now TV及ViuTV將獨家於香港播放世界盃賽事。<br />\n<br />\n世界盃將於18年6月14日揭幕，Now TV會悉數直播64場賽事，ViuTV則會免費播放19場賽事，包括揭幕戰、兩場四強和決賽。另外，兩台明晚亦會分別於Now TV632台(10:55pm)和ViuTV96台（11:00pm)直播分組賽抽籤儀式。另外，記者會雖未有公開製作成本和收費詳情，但電訊盈科媒體集團董事總經理李凱怡指未來一個月將陸續公佈收費計劃。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到免費咁多場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nVIU TV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經好耐冇轉台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企人長期TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對上一次轉個去係睇女人打拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac35203f76ecf907fc9db6a994f657e342f5ff92","tid":485311,"uid":142405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\